      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i'm doing a project for my architecture class and im stuck on cantilevered balconies. how does the balcony actually stay up if there is no support under the outer edge? i know something about moment and torque but i dont really get how the forces balance out so it doesnt just tip over.",
